Control statement : 

The statement or instruction are used to inform the computer to perform the task when a program is being executed. 

There are four types of control statemments : 

a. Sequential control statement
    input ------------------ Process ------------------ output
                     (Formula Implementation)
    Ex : p,r,t           SI = (p*r*t)/100               Ex : SI
    Ex : f               C = (f-32)*5/9                 Ex : C

b. Conditional control statement 
   (Decision control statement)
        i. if statement
        ii. if else statement
        iii. nested if else statement 
        iv. else if ladder
        
c. Switch control statement 
d. Looping control statement 